{"sn15.12:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 15.12 ","sn15.12:0.2":"2. Dutiyavagga ","sn15.12:0.3":"Sukhitasutta ","sn15.12:1.1":"Savatthiyam viharati. ","sn15.12:1.2":"“Anamataggoyam, bhikkhave, samsaro …pe… ","sn15.12:1.3":"yam, bhikkhave, passeyyatha sukhitam susajjitam, nitthamettha gantabbam: ","sn15.12:1.4":"‘amhehipi evarupam paccanubhutam imina dighena addhuna’ti. ","sn15.12:1.5":"Tam kissa hetu? ","sn15.12:1.6":"Anamataggoyam, bhikkhave, samsaro. ","sn15.12:1.7":"Pubba koti na pannayati …pe… ","sn15.12:1.8":"alam vimuccitun”ti. ","sn15.12:1.9":"Dutiyam. "}